features: Side Table with Charging Station - 3 USB ports and 2 power outlets for added convenience, which help you charge phone, desk lamp, printer within reach of your hand. 4.9ft long power cord allow you to move this end table wherever you need it while keeping your electronics charged.

Thoughtful and Friendly Design - The charging station is on the bottom shelf so that you can put your coffee on the table top safely. The black wood table is a perfect contemporary to any living room or bedroom as a mini fridge stand, nightstand, coffee table, sofa side table, printer stand.

Minimalist Modern Furniture - This square end table designed with simple straight lines and industrial style, makes it an understated elegance that fits modern to classic settings. Spacious tabletop (20" x 20") and 2-tier open shelf provide enough storage space for you. Assembled Dimensions: 20.7 in. H x 20 in. W x 20 in. L

Sturdy and Durable- Constructed of high-grade MDF board and thickened square steel frame, this nightstand is long-lasting that you can count on it to be a favorite for years to come. The metal around the wood makes it durable from any wear and tear. Weight capacity up to 110lb.

Easy to Assemble & Clean - All the assembly hardware and tools come with the modern end table. With Illustrated instructions, this black nightstand can be assembled within 5 min without effort. Adjustable footpads included ensure more stability and protecting your floor from scratches.

30 DAYS MONEY BACK: We provide 24 months warranty and lifetime professional customer service, please feel free to contact us if you have any queries no matter before or after-sales, we will reply to you within 24 hours. Get and enjoy this functional and stylish end table today!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice contemporary and sturdy end table!
reviews.reviewText: Easy to assemble. Very solid after assembly. Nice clean contemporary look. Electric outlet it comes with looks and works well and the fast charging usb ports a plus.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to put together / sturdy
reviews.reviewText: Bought these for my office and use for a printer. They work great and are perfect for what we needed

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great table for small wine cooler
reviews.reviewText: Perfect size table for a small wine cooler or refrigerator. We struggled to find a table large enough to fit our 1/2 size wine cooler but this one was a perfect match. As a bonus the built in power strip works perfect and helps conceal the cord from the refrigerator. Instructions were easy to follow with no issues. Make sure you just snug the bolts when first assembling and then tighten everything once finished. Be careful and don't overnighten the bolts holding the top shelf as they will start to bend the corner joints if overtightened. Overall good quality for the price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Use for my living room. They're sturdy and can hold a moderate amount of weight. Only gripe is that the power cord is too short (thought it would be longer).

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice little table.
reviews.reviewText: Bought this table to hold my electric humidor. It showed up nicely packaged and with a nice finish. The electric plugs is a bonus for any electronics that you might need to charge.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I loved it so much I bought a second one!
reviews.reviewText: Oh this table is JUST what I needed!! I love the space for storage on the bottom shelf. I love how big it is with plenty of room for a lamp as well as the cups and goodies my husband keeps putting on it! It's very handy to have a charging station in the living room now too. It was easy to put together and I really didn't need any help with it. I followed the directions and used the little tools that were included and it was so easy. I loved this one so much I bought another. So now I have a matching pair of tables to go with my matching lamps!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 22, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Was fairly easy to assemble (by myself) even for this senior. It’s sturdy, good quality and love the power strip for extra outlets. We put my mom’s cute little red fridge on it so it’s easier to reach and she likes the storage on the bottom shelf.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Solid Enough Table, But Outlet Died After 2 Months
reviews.reviewText: This table was easy to build, is pretty stable, and is a good enough size to support a lamp, photo frame, and speaker on the top. I like the layout of it, so overall I was satisfied with my purchase.Unfortunately, the outlet that you install in the table doesn't appear to be very reliable. Mine died abruptly after just two months. I'm trying to find a replacement part for it, but this is definitely a negative impact for my overall opinion of this piece.
Assembly was easy, looks really nice! It says two to assemble, but I had no issue putting it together myself. It was done quickly. The charging ports are a plus for my daughter.
Bien reçu l'article dans les délais prévus. Merci

reviews.reviewTitle: Livraison rapide et facile a suivre.

reviews.reviewText: Anyone with mobility issues knows how difficult it is to reach into a compact fridge when it's on the floor. This table is perfect for raising the fridge to a more practical height. Most end/side tables are too small but this one is of the perfect size 20" x 20". It's very sturdy, has a shelf and a charging station. Love it.
We have a large exo terra terrarium for our gecko and it fits perfectly on this. Its super sturdy and the extra outlets work perfectly for its lamp.
